---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Adrián Domínguez | Desarrollador";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img style="border-radius: 50%" width="250" alt="AdrianDC" src="/adrian.jpeg"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Adrián DC</h1>
    <span class="badge">Desarrollador | Músico</span>
    <h2>Acerca de mí</h2>
    <p>
        Me llamo Adrián Domínguez Casasola. Soy estudiante de ingeniería y me apasiona 
        mucho la computación y la música.
    </p>
    <p>
        Actualmente me encuentro estudiando Ingeniería Física, en la Universidad Autónoma 
        Metropolitana Unidad Azcapotzalco (UAM-A). Estoy realizando una especialidad en 
        Instrumentación y Equipo, con un enfoque en electrónica y programación.
    </p>
    <div class="center">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button class="btn">Mi portafolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills center">
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="C" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/c/c-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Cpp" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/cplusplus/cplusplus-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Arduino" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/arduino/arduino-original-wordmark.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Raspberry" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/raspberrypi/raspberrypi-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
        
    </div>
    <h2>Intereses</h2>
    <p>
        Me interesa aprender acerca de...
    </p>
</Layout>

